title: Transformers Prime - Rage of the Dinobots (01 - 04) (HD) (- Nem
description:
IDW mini-series linking the story from the "Fall of Cybertron" comic and video game to the Transformers: Prime TV show. As Cybertron Falls, the Lightning Strike Coalition now known as the Dinobots hold the line against the Decepticons. With Optimus Prime and the other Autobots on-board the Ark already gone, the rest of the population makes their escape from the dying world. Unfortunately Shockwave has plans of his own and remains behind, continuing his experiments!

Continued in Transformers Prime: Beast Hunters
